  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of the efficacy and safety of the Ventricular Pace Suppression (VpS) algorithm.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate the percentage of reduction of ventricular pacing
      using the VpS feature of the EVIA/ENTOVIS pacemaker in a controlled clinical investigation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
